Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.97,0:01:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ages since I've had that dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:25.06,0:01:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dream about when she and I met...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:35.99,0:01:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell?!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:36.99,0:01:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I'm going to dream about it,\Nat least let me see the whole thing!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:43.54,0:01:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, it's no surprise that I had that dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:47.46,0:01:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not after what happened the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.97,0:02:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all is said and done, Onodera isn't the girl I made the promise to.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only that,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.64,0:02:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but now she totally thinks that Kirisaki and I are going out.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.85,0:02:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening to me?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.19,0:02:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Young Master?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, today I'm gonna talk to Onodera and clear up this misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it was ten years ago, and you were just kids...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.78,0:02:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know. Maybe it's still important to her.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.29,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if she's still holding onto the key after all these years.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.42,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bean sprout across the street!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, darling!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.30,0:02:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you? You look pretty wiped.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, after our date the day before yesterday...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened afterwards?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.44,0:02:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Any comments about your first date?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you going on your next date?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.36,0:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They bombarded me with questions about it!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.36,0:03:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This really sucks, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even relax in my own home now!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... The only place where we can let our guard down is at school, I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How long does this have to go on?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they really mean all three years? They gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.25,0:03:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest thorn in our sides is Four-Eyes,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.51,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing as he's the only one who's not buying it at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he today?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me. I haven't seen him at all since this morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm warning you!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.10,0:03:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If, by any chance, you blow our cover at school, I'm so gonna make you regret it!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to remind me.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Another thing! Don't forget about Onodera-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you have a word with her, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.40,0:03:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If she blabs about the day before yesterday, we're screwed!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.61,0:03:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Onodera's not the kind of person who'd tell others—
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Onodera!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Ichijou-kun!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool. There's something I wanted to talk to you about.
