Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.41,0:04:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why on earth would you take this unappealing tool as your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.79,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.75,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this? You guys are dating now?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you! Must be nice to be young.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad you're sitting next to each other?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! You're jumping in too?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up a second, you guys!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all a huge misunderstanding, all right?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of good reasons—
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.07,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that my misgivings about their relationship have been confirmed,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.99,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to find a way to trip up that little punk!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait for me, please, Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swear I'll deliver you from his malevolent hands!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Claude, you idiot!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-This sucks.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by good reasons?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.59,0:05:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't tell me you two aren't actually dating.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.68,0:05:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right! You guys just didn't get it!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! We're not just any couple.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a couple that's totally hot for each other!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bold statement!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.44,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, don't give us a heart attack like that!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are sizzling!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.15,0:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We... We're screwed.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.32,0:05:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Onodera, listen. Come to think of it, I never finished what I was saying.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.41,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful! You guys just click like you're made for each other!
