Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This sucks.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.58,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does this keep happening to us?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to become of my high school life?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to mope?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's ready to wallow in depression!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.72,0:06:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to Four-Eyes staking us out during both lunch and our break time,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never did get a chance to talk to Onodera.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I have things to do,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so you go on home!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you do—
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.07,0:06:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.82,0:06:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onodera's going to think I'm taken all the way till graduation and I'll never get a chance to tell her!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.58,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, no! Anything but that! I'll try talking to her again!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I say, but I never have the chance...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:51.55,fuck me in the ass,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\c&H010101&\fnLeviBrush\pos(1112,694)}Onodera
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you about to leave, Ichijou-kun?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so. You too, Onodera?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my committee meeting just ended.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.55,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap! What a coincidence! What should I say now?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It did, huh? Sounds like a lot of work.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.43,0:07:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this is my chance! It's do or die!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't do it now, I may never get another chance to clear up this misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Onodera, could you listen to what I have to say?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, about Kirisaki and me...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, wait—what if...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.91,0:07:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right? So you two aren't actually boyfriend and girlfriend. I understand the situation now.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.12,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are you only telling me?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C-Crap! How should I answer her?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Because you're the one person that I didn't want getting the wrong idea?"
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Because I didn't want you to think about me that way?"
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, that's the same as telling her I'm in love with her!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I'm confessing either way, I don't want it to be half-assed!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And besides, I'm not mentally prepared for that yet!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap! What do I do?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.35,0:07:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, the truth is, I've been thinking that the gorilla and I aren't the best match.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering myself how we ended up together.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you go again.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say things like that!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There goes my self-esteem!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.41,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that Kirisaki-san saw something that she liked in you, don't you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.41,0:08:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, that's impossible!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there's nothing that great about me...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! There's plenty!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.72,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For real? I'm so thrilled that Onodera would praise me!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, you know...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirisaki-san still has some trouble with Japanese,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.47,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've been secretly taking notes for her. Things like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And like how you don't have it in you to ignore an abandoned animal,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.11,0:08:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or how you spend hours helping elderly women you don't even know look for things.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When your friends forget their homework,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you lie and say that you've forgotten yours too,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.53,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or when your friends are about to get busted by a teacher,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you stick with them so they don't have to get yelled at by themselves.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you there was plenty.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.83,0:08:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is like a dream. Onodera noticed me doing all those things.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, those are just little things.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kirisaki wouldn't fall for me over that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think so? But...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.89,0:09:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can understand why Kirisaki-san fell in love with you, Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. My bad!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.24,0:09:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.50,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\blur0.6\pos(914,522)\fscx130\fscy130\3c&H000000&\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\bord4\alpha&HA0&\t(755,800,\alpha&HA0&)}Episode 3: Two of a Kind
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.50,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\blur0.6\pos(909,517)\fscx130\fscy130\3c&HFFF6EF&\c&HFFF6EF&\1a&HFF&\bord4\t(755,800,\1a&H00&)}Episode 3: Two of a Kind
Dialogue: 2,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.50,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(800,0)\blur0.6\pos(909,517)\fscx130\fscy130\c&HFF7011&\3c&HFFF6EF&}Episode 3: Two of a Kind
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this key? Did Onodera drop it?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't seem to be a house key.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.55,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A key... A key? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Onodera... Is that...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's not!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.19,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is... the key... to my house—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.91,0:09:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I mean—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I mistook it for my house key!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.24,0:10:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Actually... This is... It's the key to an old bookcase in my house.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead of my house key—
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness, I'm so embarrassed! What in the world am I doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,S-S-S—
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.09,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ono—
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.22,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy crap. I've known her since middle school,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never seen Onodera act like that before.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart was about to pop out of my chest!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.73,0:10:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She said herself that it was a different key, so it's probably true.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.56,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Besides, I learned that Onodera wasn't the girl I made the promise to not too long ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I doing, getting my hopes up?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.90,0:10:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But was that really the key to a bookcase?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.88,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, crap! I forgot to explain to her what's going on between Kirisaki and me again.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, whatever. I'll just give it another shot tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure I'll get another chance.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, darling!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I really missed you!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, honey!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right back at you!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You two're so in love!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You two don't waste time, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This humiliation is too much to handle after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.87,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's only been a day. Can't expect these guys to lose interest so soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I really have to hand it to those two.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In olden times, Christianity was...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Catacombs are...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then we'll invite you next time.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.40,0:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I'll make it next time.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with all the fidgeting?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.12,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.33,0:12:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can just shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, we have to do something about Four Eyes.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.89,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he's in that mode, Claude won't listen to a word you say to him.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I guess I should let you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently Claude won't be sticking around after school today.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of deal's going down, or something.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do I have to put up with this?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, here's an idea.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.37,0:12:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a close friend who can keep a secret, you could probably tell them.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just one person,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.00,0:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if there's someone who knows what you're going through,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that would take a load off your chest too.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.80,0:13:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't you just go right ahead?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you shut up? Don't talk to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.60,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have things to do after school, so you can just head home without me!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wa—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.73,0:13:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into her now?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.11,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You want my advice? It's about Kirisaki-san, I bet.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.29,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up. These creatures called girls are as delicate as candy!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.04,0:13:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.13,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How soft are those lips of hers?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't done that yet!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What's your problem, then?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to me. I'm your best friend, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.82,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not quite clear to me, but you told her she should confide in a friend about her "secret."
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have absolutely no clue which part made her lose it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.83,0:14:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it could be that she was just in a bad mood, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, it was her way of saying,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.67,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"If I had any friends I could confide in, then I would!"
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's what it boils down to?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have any friends?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't know. You're her boyfriend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.64,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've seen her talking with the other girls like she was having a blast.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so have I,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.44,0:14:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never seen Kirisaki acting as close with others as she does with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.88,0:15:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Onodera? She already went home.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just here a minute ago, see.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently there was no committee meeting today.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.81,0:15:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So Onodera's gone home, huh? This was supposed to be my big chance!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, what should I do now?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirisaki told me to go home, so maybe I should...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.82,0:15:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I've never seen Kirisaki acting as close with others as she does with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.58,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I can't help but worry about her when you feed me a line like that!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And then, Kirisaki-san...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So I talked to her this morning again, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't shake the feeling that she's putting up a wall.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Like she's avoiding us.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.05,0:15:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard enough, trying to talk to the new girl who's both blonde and beautiful...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But she seems totally different when she's with Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.05,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind that pretty face, she might actually hate us.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ever since she transferred here,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've spent a whole lot of time with her,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.78,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I've been so preoccupied with being her fake boyfriend that
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as far as her personal life was concerned,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never even bothered to notice what was going on.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Moriya...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.59,0:16:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gan? Gan... ka?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwa... Oh, Iwashita!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, this Chinese/Japanese pronunciation thing is a total mystery.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwashita-san is the girl with the ponytail.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.89,0:16:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She's on the tennis team. Active, cheerful, and talks to me a lot.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.31,0:16:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be interested if I talk about sports.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.15,0:16:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu, too. Suzuki-san is the brunette in the Gardening Club.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's easygoing and sweet, and likes café lattes.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.74,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'm going to start up a conversation for sure!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared me!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been there?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.26,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry. I don't know, I just...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you see anything? Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.36,0:17:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait! Time out!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Go ahead and laugh!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.25,0:17:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way, since I'm still not familiar with everybody yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.29,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea how to approach them, or how to make friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no clue!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.47,0:18:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how Claude is, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.43,0:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been watching over me since I was little,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but as you've already seen, he's overprotective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.56,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\i0\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\bord4\3c&HD4BEED&\c&HD4BEED&\an7\fscx140\fscy140\move(79.53,-67.73,76.76,23.47,2,419)}Overprotective
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.56,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\i0\c&HA78492&\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\bord0\3c&HD4BEED&\an7\fscx140\fscy140\move(79.53,-67.73,76.76,23.47,2,419)}Overprotective
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.56,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I was going to school, it had to be under escort.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.15,0:18:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I was out, he'd be skulking around, packing a gun!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.77,0:18:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, he started checking out who I was hanging with.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea how hard he made it for me to make friends!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.45,0:18:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I wanted to make friends like any normal girl and lead a peaceful life.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that if I came to Japan,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.25,0:18:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,no one would know that I was the daughter of\Na gang boss, and I would finally get a real shot at it.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.17,0:18:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not working out for me, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.22,0:18:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I telling this to you of all people?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, this is one messed-up story.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess if you're brought up in the same environment,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you start to think like each other, too, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.98,0:18:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to have a notebook like yours too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's in the yakuza, you know. So since I was a little kid,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.53,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,every time I changed schools, people would say all kinds of things about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.24,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a notebook to help me overcome it.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwashita's a good kid, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you bring up sports in front of her, she gets totally fired up.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.84,0:19:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki's a good student, so you should ask her if you don't get something.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you'd get along really well with Moriya.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure she's been dying to talk to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.14,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know pretty much everything about our class from all my past experiences.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I've made so many notebooks.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.65,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd be happy to help you out. You know, with your notebook.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.15,0:19:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not like you, but that doesn't mean I don't get how you feel.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.75,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? If you're gonna insist like that, then I think I might as well let you help me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have no clue how to act cute, do you?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you expect?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.01,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I act all cute as if I were your real girlfriend?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.81,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When all is said and done, we're just actors!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, show me your notes for a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to. Why do I have to show you?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.61,Alternate,,0,0,0,,C'mon, show me! I'll check them for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to—Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.82,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actors?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is my entry nothing but insults?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't read a young girl's notes without permission!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, it wouldn't kill you to say something good about me!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actors...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are they talking about?
