Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Onodera-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This happens every time right before she shows up.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.52,0:20:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ichijou-kun and Kirisaki-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped by to give you a hand!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, guys!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're letting you out today?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.45,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feelings for them really aren't mutual, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.86,0:21:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No. But that's okay. Only because it's Onodera.
